.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Birthday: june, december, august, january, november
Food: cabbage, orange, corn, onion, pomegranate
Game: monopoly, canasta, mah-jongg, domino, go
Hobby: photography, hiking, writing, drawing, woodworking
1. Birthday:june == Color:red
2. Birthday:swedish == Hobby:writing
3. Birthday:december == Food:onion
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Food:orange
6. Game:mah-jongg == Hobby:hiking
7. Color:yellow == Game:canasta
8. Food:corn is in the middle
9. Birthday:january is on the far left
10. Game:go is on the left or right of Hobby:photography
11. Hobby:woodworkings is on the left or right of Game:canasta
12. Game:monopoly == Food:cabbage
13. Birthday:august == Game:domino
14. Birthday:january is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Game:go is on the left or right of Food:pomegranate

